parameters:
Underling: Now that Shark Broccoli-sama is becoming the
mayor and leaving the organization, I've inherited the
detailed recipe for the delicious powder. From now on, I'll
be the one to protect the taste of our organization...!

Memimi: Hmm, you've been in charge of making the delicious
powder for quite a long time... Well then, let me check the
taste with my keen tongue... Hand me a pinch!
Underling: Really, you love snacking, don't you...

Underling: (When I see Shark Broccoli-sama eating, it
reminds me... That adorable tongue of his licking my ass...
It was a terrifying torture, but he even gave me a handjob,
and it felt really good...)

Memimi: Munch munch... Hmm, this is even better than
before... Not bad at all... Munch munch...

Underling: Lord Shark has unified all the organizations in
the city and ascended to the seat of the new grand boss...
It turns out that the mysterious female fiend who was
originally a part-time worker named Samesan, and from there,
even more has happened, it's hard for my feelings to keep
up.

Memimi: These past few months have been utterly hectic. The
environment surrounding me has changed quite a bit. You
underlings in charge of the hideout's core haven't changed
much though...

Underling: Oh, I'm happy to be with Lord Shark even if my
position has changed...! Please, go out with me...! I've
been smitten with you ever since we worked the same shift at
the convenience store...

Memimi: Sorry, but I'm not interested in that sort of thing
right now. Let's continue to work hard together without
changing our relationship...

Underling: I thought I might be rejected, but you're used to
turning people down, huh...

Underling: (Well, after all, I've had sex with Lord Shark
several times, even if it was under orders from the mayor.
Such unimaginable things can happen... Surely my chance to
date will come!!)

Memimi: I can tell exactly what you're thinking... Every
time we talk, you can't be satisfied without recalling my
lewd behavior, can you...?

Underling: Even though you've unified all the organizations
in the city and our numbers have increased, is it really
okay not to take any tribute? If you wished, Lord Shark
could be receiving a tremendous amount of money every
month...

Memimi: From the start, this business isn't about money...
We've taken control over all the hustles in the city, but we
let those without any illegal aspects continue as before,
without skimming anything off the top...

Underling: Despite having such incredible power, you never
use it for yourself, still working shifts at the convenience
store to pay for tuition... Lord Shark is untainted by
corruption...

Memimi: I won't say I'm uninterested in money, but when
humans become too fixated on it, nothing good comes of it.
Having an amount that fits one's station is enough...

Underling: Even the vast sum of money that the former mayor
made by getting Lord Shark to appear in an adult video was
promptly donated to the city. That video sold at a legendary
level; the amount was obscene...

Memimi: I wouldn't want to keep such money for myself...! I
wanted to forget about it quickly, so I donated it in a
hurry! Uwaaaah...

Underling: Come to think of it, Lord Shark Duke was
originally one of the Four Heavenly Kings, right?... I've
never seen the other three...

Memimi: I accidentally damaged the monster suit, and while
waiting for it to be repaired, everything came to an end...
If they had been here, things might have gone more
smoothly... It was bad timing...
